:46:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbtw以前好似可以由荃灣廣播個邊行去西鐵</blockquote><br />\n宜家兜地面都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw唔知係咪記錯 但印象中以前西鐵站有橋駁去灣景</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西鐵站灣景隔離咪有棟野係地面做小巴站既<br />\n個棟野係政府<br />\n有天橋係荃廣接祈德尊接個棟野接西鐵<br />\n灣景都好似有天橋接個棟野<br />\n好耐無行所以我都唔知呢幾條天橋仲存唔存在啦<br />\n個棟野以前係搞身份證個類入境野<br />\n十幾年前荒廢左之後就無再用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拆左n 世啦<br />\n樓都起左一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a325b36ae1653ef9263f8bdee96d0578e04b75","tid":45061,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T23:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbtw以前好似可以由荃灣廣播個邊行去西鐵</blockquote><br />\n宜家兜地面都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw唔知係咪記錯 但印象中以前西鐵站有橋駁去灣景</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西鐵站灣景隔離咪有棟野係地面做小巴站既<br />\n個棟野係政府<br />\n有天橋係荃廣接祈德尊接個棟野接西鐵<br />\n灣景都好似有天橋接個棟野<br />\n好耐無行所以我都唔知呢幾條天橋仲存唔存在啦<br />\n個棟野以前係搞身份證個類入境野<br />\n十幾年前荒廢左之後就無再用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拆左n 世啦<br />\n樓都起左一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果個叫「荃灣運輸大樓」，而家成為華𢡟豪宅樓盤連商場之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb3e97840836286e2890967975602d9c20e5786","tid":45061,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T23:53:08.000Z","msg":"utravel 好似吹奏過荃灣係乜鳩天空之城 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e2c3ed88393c95225728a38a3054b0e669946f","tid":45061,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T23:55:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實係規劃得差先要補起天橋搭救。<br />\n<br />\n仲講屈機.... 成個荃灣根本無美感可言。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺0美感<br />\n但無可否認係方便左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成個區好嘔心"},{"pid":"87c356ad9df0145c76f32d4918079ae7c03e6c60","tid":45061,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T00:01:23.000Z","msg":"遲d 仲多商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> citywalk 2期隔離又起酒店同甲級商業大厦，同樓，"},{"pid":"6ee0e488c28a72412b5efd326877387fe9c51bf8","tid":45061,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T00:04:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n條橋真係會震<br />\n成日係個條橋行行下會覺得暈暈地咁<br />\n有次停左係條橋到先feel到成條橋原來真係震緊</blockquote><br />\n屌真係震架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我之前都feel過以為自己攰得濟暈暈地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家陣唔夠薑行個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條天橋之前起好左都要廷遲開就知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我都係照行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前起好左話燒焊有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以延期"},{"pid":"5d609ba6fa1ebadc25b4ae409093537798cddcdb","tid":45061,"uid":22863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T00:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n宜家兜地面都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw唔知係咪記錯 但印象中以前西鐵站有橋駁去灣景</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西鐵站灣景隔離咪有棟野係地面做小巴站既<br />\n個棟野係政府<br />\n有天橋係荃廣接祈德尊接個棟野接西鐵<br />\n灣景都好似有天橋接個棟野<br />\n好耐無行所以我都唔知呢幾條天橋仲存唔存在啦<br />\n個棟野以前係搞身份證個類入境野<br />\n十幾年前荒廢左之後就無再用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拆左n 世啦<br />\n樓都起左一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十世都無昂高頭望過真係唔知佢拆左<br />\n戇鳩左唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cea4f7d492ccf9ef73f0464c4ad4adcf6058078","tid":45061,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T00:27:47.000Z","msg":"返灣仔住荃灣，落狗屎都無拎遮返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c80cac4b7672b64e93bf84fe5f46c0d9aa9f039","tid":45061,"uid":35421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T00:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔覺<br />\n有幾條起得好多舊魚<br />\n大河道個條聽人話會震<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好震<br />\n震到個人feed到軟一軟咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未入荃新天地前<br />\n落斜果個位 我仲以為地震<br />\n打過去投訴冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeecbeb2aa55d18b1299a25d6f92867ceb928bf3","tid":45061,"uid":22889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:43:35.000Z","msg":"亂鳩咁起呢方面係幾屈機既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先唔講完全冇美感可言<br />\n南豐去匯豐/吉野家嗰段真係唔知做乜鳩 同地鐵站嗰到重疊晒（有行開應該知我講邊）<br />\nBtw中環嗰啲先叫屈機"},{"pid":"a16b611627f622282174469f00899f715d42dd46","tid":45061,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:46:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好震<br />\n震到個人feed到軟一軟咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未入荃新天地前<br />\n落斜果個位 我仲以為地震<br />\n打過去投訴冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌，我都係！ 以為係我就暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa26e022379ff188d242e544971e46141cedafc3","tid":45061,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔覺<br />\n有幾條起得好多舊魚<br />\n大河道個條聽人話會震<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好震<br />\n震到個人feed到軟一軟咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未入荃新天地前<br />\n落斜果個位 我仲以為地震<br />\n打過去投訴冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係咪荃新行去荃灣站個一段<br />\n有次夜晚行行下feel到震左幾野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開頭係高登聽人話條橋用料唔好有問題<br />\n原來係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023e2937024a6953a1f943ff08671ad260b4def3","tid":45061,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:50:35.000Z","msg":"最憎行天橋"},{"pid":"d029875e719d4af09133f70d2133cf1d028df2cd","tid":45061,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:55:15.000Z","msg":"我覺得幾方便既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06b73c72f5d2e35d2389e41cb73e680b0d16fc0","tid":45061,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:56:38.000Z","msg":"成日浦開荃灣撚表示 荃灣唔撚係人住"},{"pid":"839adc1f9393bb50307a564b95b74507e2d056ef","tid":45061,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:58:22.000Z","msg":"之前晌荃灣站行去荃灣廣場果邊<br />\n兜到傻又多馬路<br />\n依家方便好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072b27c195ca2c4f47c754d680b0510e610c7ce4","tid":45061,"uid":67085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔覺<br />\n有幾條起得好多舊魚<br />\n大河道個條聽人話會震<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得會震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e935bbca07498d34039a26769f5ef0f86dcf3a23","tid":45061,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:21:03.000Z","msg":"傳聞條橋個頂去水有問題，一落狗屎會養水，有倒塌危機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\